Router/Resource version 0.21
============================

This library's module, Router::Resource, provides an REST-friendly interface for
creating routes.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, type the following:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install

Or, if you don't have Module::Build installed, type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

Dependencies
------------

Router::Resource requires the following modules:

* Test::Builder 0.17
* XML::LibXML 1.69

